to medical and prescription drug benefits in 2021 compared to $3,293 in 2020. In addition, in 2021, we prefunded $685 for
future benefit payments versus $745 in 2020. We paid $5,942 of pension benefits out of plan assets in 2021 compared to
$5,124 in 2020.
