arrangement prescribe substantive non-proportionate cash distributions, both from operations and in liquidation, that are based on
classes of interests held by investors. In the event that DIRECTV records a loss, that loss will be allocated to ownership interests
based on their seniority, beginning with the most subordinated interests.
